[if {EXPRESSION}
   ...
else if {EXPRESSION}
   ...
else if {EXPRESSION}
   ...
else
   ...]

[if {EXPRESSION}
   ...
otherwise if {EXPRESSION}
   ...
otherwise if {EXPRESSION}
   ...
otherwise
   ...]

[[If]] blocks are defined as known from pretty much any other language. [[Otherwise]] and [[else]] are synonyms for each other and can even be mixed in the same [[if]] block.
